<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Duiker, Tweefontein issue cautionary.</title>
<headline>Duiker, Tweefontein issue cautionary.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-08-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>South Africa's Duiker Mining Ltd and Tweefontein United Collieries Ltd said on Tuesday they were in talks which, if successfully concluded, could have an effect on their share prices.</p>
<p>They advised shareholders to exercise caution in their sharedealings until further notice.</p>
<p>No further details were given.</p>
<p>Tweefontein Collieries is a division of Duiker Mining, which is a member of the Lonrho plc group of companies.</p>
